157
00:13:10,149 --> 00:13:12,150
Mr. Suga...?

158
00:13:15,606 --> 00:13:18,314
Mr. Suga?

159
00:13:26,906 --> 00:13:28,899
No, I shouldn't be doing this.

160
00:13:28,924 --> 00:13:30,352
Mm. Hello.

161
00:13:30,432 --> 00:13:32,727
I-I'm so sorry.

162
00:13:32,775 --> 00:13:34,562
Oh, you're the new assistant.

163
00:13:34,689 --> 00:13:35,993
Kei told me about you.

164
00:13:36,088 --> 00:13:37,400
What? No, I haven't...

165
00:13:37,550 --> 00:13:39,402
I'm Natsumi. Welcome.

166
00:13:39,465 --> 00:13:39,791
Huh?

167
00:13:39,894 --> 00:13:43,501
Finally, he's found someone to do all my grunt work.

168
00:13:47,953 --> 00:13:49,898
So, uh, kid...

169
00:13:49,961 --> 00:13:51,931
Uh, yeah?

170
00:13:53,298 --> 00:13:54,693
I saw you checking out my boobs.

171
00:13:54,718 --> 00:13:55,776
No, I wasn't.

172
00:13:57,817 --> 00:13:59,438
Okay, kid, what's your name?

173
00:13:59,538 --> 00:14:00,900
Hodaka Morishima.

174
00:14:01,014 --> 00:14:03,220
Hodaka, huh? That's interesting.

175
00:14:03,419 --> 00:14:05,590
Are you one of Mr. Suga's employees?

176
00:14:05,615 --> 00:14:07,945
Oh, so you want to know the truth about us?

177
00:14:07,980 --> 00:14:08,484
Yeah.

178
00:14:09,016 --> 00:14:10,024
Hilarious.

179
00:14:11,095 --> 00:14:13,558
I know what you're thinking, and you're right.

180
00:14:15,457 --> 00:14:16,560
I don't believe it.

181
00:14:17,284 --> 00:14:19,048
I've never met a mistress before.

182
00:14:20,319 --> 00:14:21,073
Huh.

183
00:14:21,908 --> 00:14:23,950
Long time, no see, little man.

184
00:14:24,069 --> 00:14:25,028
Did you lose weight?

185
00:14:25,052 --> 00:14:25,547
For me?

186
00:14:27,121 --> 00:14:29,695
Let me guess... This from playing pachinko?

187
00:14:31,665 --> 00:14:33,286
So, little man,

188
00:14:33,453 --> 00:14:35,288
you came for a job... am I right?

189
00:14:36,514 --> 00:14:38,650
This is basically what we do here.

190
00:14:38,793 --> 00:14:42,447
