191
00:14:45,409 --> 00:14:47,388
We're doing a piece on urban legends.

192
00:14:47,864 --> 00:14:50,686
All you got to do is talk to a
few people who have witnessed some.

193
00:14:50,742 --> 00:14:51,780
It'll be a piece of cake.

194
00:14:51,804 --> 00:14:52,750
Huh? I'm not...

195
00:14:52,775 --> 00:14:54,292
It can be on anything.

196
00:14:54,507 --> 00:14:57,223
Doomsday predictions, abductions, you know.

197
00:14:57,620 --> 00:14:59,622
Whatever you kids are into these days.

198
00:15:00,043 --> 00:15:01,013
Here. I got one.

199
00:15:01,497 --> 00:15:04,468
"The girl who brings sunshine wherever she goes."

200
00:15:04,493 --> 00:15:05,348
S-Sunshine girl?

201
00:15:05,372 --> 00:15:06,472
Bring that sunshine!

202
00:15:06,497 --> 00:15:08,639
Yeah, it's been raining so damn much this year.

203
00:15:08,664 --> 00:15:10,185
She's got to be in demand.

204
00:15:10,215 --> 00:15:10,946
Right?

205
00:15:11,395 --> 00:15:12,287
Okay.

206
00:15:12,517 --> 00:15:14,712
Come on, little man. Where's your hustle?

207
00:15:15,059 --> 00:15:16,767
She's already got a thing set up.

208
00:15:16,918 --> 00:15:18,448
Tag along. Take notes.

209
00:15:18,496 --> 00:15:18,909
Huh?

210
00:15:19,013 --> 00:15:20,434
Wait, what? Like, like, now?

211
00:15:20,482 --> 00:15:22,099
Oh, it'll be like an audition!

212
00:15:22,123 --> 00:15:22,746
A what?

213
00:15:23,023 --> 00:15:25,555
I don't think that's a good idea.

214
00:15:26,851 --> 00:15:27,883
Of course.

215
00:15:28,232 --> 00:15:29,867
Sunshine girls do exist.

216
00:15:29,891 --> 00:15:30,638
I knew it!

217
00:15:31,149 --> 00:15:33,254
But rain girls exist as well.

218
00:15:34,024 --> 00:15:36,663
The former are protected by a fox spirit,

219
00:15:36,845 --> 00:15:39,340
and the latter are protected by a dragon god.

220
00:15:39,864 --> 00:15:41,036
Uh, what?

221
00:15:41,286 --> 00:15:44,504
Those who are protected by the
dragon god tend to drink a lot.

222
00:15:44,806 --> 00:15:46,095
They yearn for water.

223
00:15:46,120 --> 00:15:49,480
They're strong-willed and competitive,
though careless and unreliable.

224
00:15:50,149 --> 00:15:51,415
That kind of sounds like me.

225
00:15:51,450 --> 00:15:53,730
Those protected by the fox spirit are hardworking

226
00:15:53,904 --> 00:15:55,487
but too timid to be leaders.

227
00:15:55,709 --> 00:15:57,593
Though many of them are quite beautiful.

228
00:15:57,640 --> 00:15:58,539
That's totally me.

229
