The four spirits of weather are off-balance, so
more sunshine and rain girls are born these days.

230
00:16:03,295 --> 00:16:05,613
It's the homeostasis of Gaia theory.

231
00:16:05,638 --> 00:16:06,703
That's how it works.

232
00:16:06,728 --> 00:16:08,602
But one must be careful.

233
00:16:09,277 --> 00:16:12,765
Whenever we mess with nature, we will always pay a price.

234
00:16:13,045 --> 00:16:15,697
And they say whoever uses too much weather power

235
00:16:15,803 --> 00:16:17,223
will get spirited away.

236
00:16:17,303 --> 00:16:17,779
I see.

237
00:16:17,866 --> 00:16:18,445
Huh?

238
00:16:19,104 --> 00:16:21,735
Don't worry. I'll be careful.

239
00:16:21,902 --> 00:16:23,100
So...

240
00:16:23,132 --> 00:16:24,404
how did it go?

241
00:16:25,954 --> 00:16:30,895
