stuff that came straight out of a fantasy novel.

242
00:16:31,157 --> 00:16:33,056
Weather power making you disappear.

243
00:16:33,127 --> 00:16:34,423
Yeah, sure. Typical.

244
00:16:34,534 --> 00:16:36,830
