248
00:16:46,371 --> 00:16:47,417
Damn, you're slow.

249
00:16:47,499 --> 00:16:48,272
I'm sorry.

250
00:16:48,690 --> 00:16:51,663
Well, at least your writing style's not too bad.

251
00:16:52,061 --> 00:16:53,634
