266
00:17:14,085 --> 00:17:16,890
Now, here's to our new hire,

267
00:17:17,049 --> 00:17:18,185
Hodaka.

268
00:17:18,337 --> 00:17:19,456
Bottoms up.

269
00:17:20,482 --> 00:17:22,640
Slow down, Hodaka.

270
00:17:23,149 --> 00:17:28,328
It was the first meal I had shared
with anyone since I came to Tokyo.

271
00:17:28,550 --> 00:17:31,300
And that is how my new life began.

